Package: DLabLinguistics
Title: Analysis of linguistically embeded text components created by the Linguistics Swift package.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rodney", "Dyer", , "rodney@dyerlab.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is an analysis package for linguistic data derived from the Dyerlab Linguistics 
    Swift package.  The purpose of this package is to perform differential analysis of compositional, 
    natural language, and transformer-based embeddings on components of scientific reserach manuscripts.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
